in order to make a full stack app deployable to the cloud you need to:
1. create images using Dockerfile
2. tag images and upload them to the Docker hub
3. create a docker-compose.yml that will bundle front and backend together

docker build -t ngtetris-frontent .  ---- build an image from Dockerfile in current directory
docker images - lists all images
docker tag ae7 jarek104/ngtetris-frontend:mvp -- tags the image as mvp
docker push jarek104/ngtetris-frontend:mvp -- pushes to docker hub
